can I get another?

31:36.416 --> 31:39.723
ALL:
Amen.

31:39.767 --> 31:44.554
My mom passed away
a few years ago

31:44.598 --> 31:46.034
in a hit-and-run
accident

31:46.078 --> 31:48.428
when I was
still a teenager,

31:48.471 --> 31:50.082
and it's the talks
I had with her

31:50.125 --> 31:52.911
I cherish more than anything.

31:52.954 --> 31:58.307
I remember her telling me...

31:58.351 --> 32:01.745
that it was Aunt Sally
who took us in

32:01.789 --> 32:08.448
when I was just a baby,
after my father died in Vietnam.

32:08.491 --> 32:09.405
[ sighing]

32:09.449 --> 32:11.451
I'll always love her for that.

32:11.494 --> 32:14.410
Your mama dead, too?

32:14.454 --> 32:16.543
He just said it.

32:22.462 --> 32:23.767
Young man,

32:23.811 --> 32:26.770
I'm so glad that you came
for your aunt's funeral.

32:26.814 --> 32:27.554
Yeah.

32:27.597 --> 32:28.685
