32:33.212 --> 32:34.996
[ chuckling]

32:35.040 --> 32:36.519
What was it?

32:36.563 --> 32:37.999
What was what?

32:38.043 --> 32:39.218
Your job.

32:39.261 --> 32:42.003
It's funny, she never mentioned
what it was.

32:42.047 --> 32:44.049
Boy, I haven't
seen you

32:44.092 --> 32:46.312
