to a grasshopper.

32:46.355 --> 32:50.620
Reverend, um, have you seen
this very pretty lady--

32:50.664 --> 32:51.970
I think her name is Lilly?

32:52.013 --> 32:53.101
She ain't no lady.

32:53.145 --> 32:55.321
Oh, now, Mother Cooley.

32:55.364 --> 32:58.106
All sinners are welcome
in the house of the Lord.

32:58.150 --> 32:59.499
Sinner? She's a sinner?

32:59.542 --> 33:00.891
What kind of sinner?

33:00.935 --> 33:03.764
Unrepentant.

33:03.807 --> 33:04.808
Really.

33:04.852 --> 33:06.201
