Well, Darrin,
I just come

33:06.245 --> 33:07.811
to offer you my condolences
and to just let you know

33:07.855 --> 33:11.990
that to be absent from the body
is to be present with the Lord.

33:12.033 --> 33:14.949
You got to understand
that she's in

33:14.993 --> 33:16.603
a far better place, okay?

33:16.646 --> 33:17.952
Yes, ma'am.

33:17.996 --> 33:19.258
