the Crisco measurements by half.

33:42.020 --> 33:44.283
Don't change
that Chicken Supreme.

33:44.326 --> 33:45.849
[ chuckling]

33:45.893 --> 33:49.070
And to
Paulina Pritchett,

33:49.114 --> 33:51.507
I leave my collection
of church hats

33:51.551 --> 33:53.379
that she always
complimented me on.

33:53.422 --> 33:56.295
She should really enjoy
wearing them,

33:56.338 --> 33:58.688
unless, of course, she was lying
to me all those years

33:58.732 --> 34:01.865
but criticizing my taste
behind my back.

34:05.347 --> 34:08.089
I'll wear them every Sunday.

34:09.569 --> 34:14.181
And now,
for my only surviving relative,

34:14.226 --> 34:17.228
my great-nephew, Darrin.

34:17.272 --> 34:20.536
To Darrin,
I leave the box

34:20.580 --> 34:22.451
containing the letters
his mother sent me

34:22.495 --> 34:24.192
after they left Monte Carlo.

34:24.235 --> 34:25.367
I also
pass on to him

34:25.411 --> 34:28.978
