anyone, but, um...

35:43.315 --> 35:46.535
I'm a music producer.

35:46.579 --> 35:47.580
Oh.

35:47.623 --> 35:49.408
Yeah, that's what
I do for a living.

35:49.451 --> 35:51.758
Ooh, looks like Sally
might have been onto something.

35:51.801 --> 35:54.456
