versus West Coast thing.

36:07.904 --> 36:10.472
Yeah, I just sat them all down
and made them watch Roots.

36:10.516 --> 36:13.214
I think
I read about that.

36:13.258 --> 36:15.564
So, what
is this Gospel Explosion?

36:15.608 --> 36:16.826
Oh, it's the annual event

36:16.870 --> 36:19.220
where choirs
from all over the southeast

36:19.264 --> 36:20.395
come to Columbus, Georgia,

36:20.439 --> 36:23.355
to compete for the best
gospel performance

36:23.398 --> 36:24.878
and a $10,000 cash prize.

36:24.921 --> 36:26.314
[ chuckling]

36:26.358 --> 36:27.663
Yeah, a prize that could pay

36:27.707 --> 36:31.145
