musical producer

36:35.018 --> 36:36.324
would bring it home, yes?

36:36.368 --> 36:39.458
Paul Lewis, have you lost
your natural mind?

36:39.501 --> 36:40.676
I wish Mama was alive

36:40.720 --> 36:42.330
to see how you turn
on family like this.

36:42.374 --> 36:43.679
Sally was as close to family
as anybody can get,

36:43.723 --> 36:45.507
