about your job.

01:31:09.115 --> 01:31:10.290
She did?

01:31:10.334 --> 01:31:11.814
Oh, we got our
record deal already?

01:31:11.857 --> 01:31:14.120
No, no, no, he's
not a record producer.

01:31:14.164 --> 01:31:19.604
