other firm with ideas

01:31:48.590 --> 01:31:50.330
as good as yours.

01:31:50.374 --> 01:31:51.897
That's a good thing.

01:31:51.941 --> 01:31:54.117
They said they're
willing to sign on

01:31:54.160 --> 01:31:55.553
as clients, but only if

01:31:55.597 --> 01:31:57.816
