01:32:23.233 --> 01:32:24.277
Boy, don't you know

01:32:24.321 --> 01:32:27.280
once you go gospel,
you can't go back.

01:32:27.324 --> 01:32:29.195
God don't like ugly.

01:32:29.239 --> 01:32:30.370
Look at Sam Cooke.

01:32:30.414 --> 01:32:33.112
Left the church,
few years later...

01:32:33.156 --> 01:32:34.549
